; Cinder Vaults — Sunken Reading Chamber.
; W3-T7 Stage 4 — S2 chunk authoring (ticket 86c9y7ygj).
;
; Role: the NPC-anchor chunk for `s2_z2_reading_chamber` (the order's
; functional habitable space per palette-stratum-2.md §1.6 — 50% Cinder
; substrate, 50% Archive overlay). Low-pressure beat: a single
; Sunken-Scholar guards the reading-desk shape. Future Part E NPC dialogue
; tree wiring will attach here.
;
; Mob mix: 1 Sunken-Scholar (lone reading-desk guardian — the scholar who
; got too absorbed in their study to leave when the seam-break came).
;
; Ports: WEST entry + EAST exit, standard mating shape.

